  "title": "Warehouse cum Delivery Attendant x 5 (West/ 5 days/ Gross up to $2500/ Transport pick-up) [R22107578]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Summary:</strong></p>\n<p>※ Location: Tuas (Company pick-up transport provided)<br>\n※ 5days work week<br>\n※ Gross salary up to $2500<br>\n※ AWS + Bonus provided</p>\n<p>※ On job training provided</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong><br>\n※ Follow &amp; assist driver in delivery of company's goods<br>\n※ Loading &amp; unloading of goods</p>\n<p>※ Picking and packing, perform inventory checking/ stock take</p>\n<p>※ Ensure the cleanliness of warehouse<br>\n※ Ad-hoc assignment given by Supervisor</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong><br>\nGood working attitude and able to start work within short notice</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>To Apply, kindly click on the \"APPLY NOW\" button<br>\nWe regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Staffking Pte Ltd (20C0358) | Jasmine Wong (R22107578)</p>",
